                    <div className="space-y-1">
                      {linkTypes.filter(lt => lt.category === 'School Breaks').map(linkType => (

                            type="checkbox"

                      üíº Business Tools
                    </h4>
                    <div className="space-y-1">
                      {linkTypes.filter(lt => lt.category === 'Business Tools').map(linkType => (
                        <label key={linkType.id} className="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-xs">
                          <input
                            type="checkbox"
                            checked={selectedLinkTypes.includes(linkType.id)}
                            onChange={() => toggleLinkType(linkType.id)}
                            className="rounded w-4 h-4"
                            style={{ accentColor: theme.colors.primary }}
                          />
                          <span className="text-sm">{linkType.emoji}</span>
                          <span className="text-gray-700 font-medium">{linkType.label}</span>
                        </label>
                      ))}

                  </div>

                  {/* CATCH-ALL: Any remaining categories */}

                    <h4 className="font-semibold text-sm text-purple-800 mb-2 flex items-center gap-1">
                      ‚≠ê Other
                    </h4>
                    <div className="space-y-1">
                      {linkTypes.filter(lt => !['Portal (iClass)', 'Programs', 'General Info', 'Summer Camp', 'Trials & Pricing', 'School Breaks', 'Business Tools'].includes(lt.category)).map(linkType => (
                        <label key={linkType.id} className="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-xs">
                          <input
                            type="checkbox"
                            checked={selectedLinkTypes.includes(linkType.id)}
                            onChange={() => toggleLinkType(linkType.id)}
                            className="rounded w-4 h-4"
                            style={{ accentColor: theme.colors.primary }}
                          />
                          <span className="text-sm">{linkType.emoji}</span>
                          <span className="text-gray-700 font-medium">{linkType.label}</span>
                        </label>
                      ))}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                </div>

                {/* Quick Action Buttons */}
                <div className="flex gap-2 mb-4">
                  <button
                    onClick={() => setSelectedLinkTypes(linkTypes.map(lt => lt.id))}
                    className="flex-1 px-3 py-2 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded text-sm hover:bg-green-200 transition-colors"
                  >
                    ‚úÖ Select All
                  </button>
                  <button
                    onClick={() => setSelectedLinkTypes([])}
                    className="flex-1 px-3 py-2 bg-red-100 text-red-700 rounded text-sm hover:bg-red-200 transition-colors"
                  >
                    ‚ùå Clear All
                  </button>
                </div>

                {/* BOTTOM COPY BUTTON - No scrolling needed! */}
                <button
                  onClick={bulkCopyLinks}
                  disabled={selectedGyms.length === 0 || selectedLinkTypes.length === 0}
                  className={`w-full p-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-base transition-all duration-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 ${
                    selectedGyms.length > 0 && selectedLinkTypes.length > 0
                      ? 'text-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] transform'
                      : 'text-gray-400 bg-gray-100 cursor-not-allowed'
                  }`}
                  style={{ 
                    background: selectedGyms.length > 0 && selectedLinkTypes.length > 0
                      ? `linear-gradient(135deg, ${theme.colors.primary} 0%, #d4a5a5 100%)`
                      : '#f3f4f6',
                    border: '2px solid',
                    borderColor: selectedGyms.length > 0 && selectedLinkTypes.length > 0
                      ? theme.colors.primary
                      : '#d1d5db'
                  }}
                >
                  <Copy className="w-5 h-5" />
                  {selectedGyms.length > 0 && selectedLinkTypes.length > 0 
                    ? `üöÄ COPY NOW (${selectedGyms.length} gyms √ó ${selectedLinkTypes.length} types)`
                    : 'üéØ Select gyms & link types above'
                  }
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Search Bar */}
        <div className="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-4 mb-6" style={{ borderColor: '#d5c2c2', border: '1px solid' }}>
          <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div className="relative flex-1">
              <Search className="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 absolute left-3 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2" />
              <input
                type="text"
                placeholder="Search gyms by name or location..."
                value={searchTerm}
                onChange={(e) => setSearchTerm(e.target.value)}
                className="w-full rounded px-10 py-2 text-sm"
                style={{ borderColor: '#d5c2c2', border: '1px solid' }}
              />
            </div>
            <button 
              className="flex items-center gap-1 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded text-xs transition-colors"
              style={{ backgroundColor: theme.colors.primary }}
            >
              <RefreshCw className="w-3 h-3" />
              Refresh
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Results */}
        <div className="mb-4">
          <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">üè≠ Factory Results</h2>
            <div className="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium text-white" style={{ backgroundColor: theme.colors.primary }}>
              ‚ú® {filteredGyms.length} results
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="space-y-8">
            {filteredGyms.map(gym => (
              <div key={gym.id} id={`gym-${gym.id}`} className="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden" style={{ borderColor: '#d5c2c2', border: '1px solid' }}>
                {/* Gym Header */}
                <div className="text-white p-3 relative" style={{ background: `linear-gradient(to right, ${theme.colors.primary}, #A38F85)` }}>
                  <div className="absolute top-2 right-16 text-lg animate-pulse">‚ú®</div>
                  <div className="flex items-center justify-between relative z-10">
                    <h3 className="text-lg font-bold">{gym.name}</h3>
                    <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
                      <button
                        onClick={scrollToTop}
                        className="bg-white bg-opacity-20 hover:bg-opacity-30 p-2 rounded-full transition-all"
                        title="Back to top"
                      >
                        <ArrowUp className="w-4 h-4" />
                      </button>
                      <div className="text-sm font-medium" style={{ color: '#f0e6e6' }}>{gym.id.toUpperCase()}</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div className="flex items-center gap-4 mt-1 text-xs" style={{ color: '#f0e6e6' }}>
                    <div className="flex items-center gap-1">
                      <MapPin className="w-3 h-3" />
                      <span>{gym.address}</span>
                      <Copy 
                        className="w-3 h-3 cursor-pointer hover:text-white transition-colors" 
                        onClick={() => copyContactInfo(gym.address, 'Address')}
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div className="flex items-center gap-1">
                      <Phone className="w-3 h-3" />
                      <span>{gym.phone}</span>
                      <Copy 
                        className="w-3 h-3 cursor-pointer hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        onClick={() => copyContactInfo(gym.phone, 'Phone')}
                      />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                {/* Links Grid - 5 Columns */}
                <div className="p-6">
                  <div className="grid grid-cols-5 gap-4">
                    {linkTypes.map(linkType => {
                      const url = getGymLink(gym.id, linkType.id);
                      const isSelected = selectedGymLinks[gym.id]?.includes(linkType.id) || false;
                      const isEditing = editingLink?.gymId === gym.id && editingLink?.linkTypeId === linkType.id;
                      
                      return (
                        <div key={linkType.id} className={`p-4 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 ${
                          url 
                            ? 'hover:bg-gray-50 hover:shadow-sm' 
                            : 'bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100'
                        } ${isSelected ? 'bg-blue-50 shadow-sm' : ''}`}
                        style={{ 
                          borderColor: isSelected ? theme.colors.primary : '#d5c2c2', 
                          border: '1px solid',
                          minHeight: '88px'
                        }}>
                          
                          {/* Edit Mode */}
                          {isEditing ? (
                            <div className="space-y-1">
                              <div className="flex items-center gap-1">
                                <span className="text-base">{linkType.emoji}</span>
                                <span className="text-xs font-medium text-gray-900">{linkType.label}</span>
                              </div>
                              <input
                                type="text"
                                value={editValue}
                                onChange={(e) => setEditValue(e.target.value)}
                                placeholder="Enter URL or info..."
                                className="w-full text-xs p-1 border rounded"
                                style={{ borderColor: '#d5c2c2' }}
                                autoFocus
                              />
                              <div className="flex items-center gap-1">
                                <button
                                  onClick={saveEditedLink}
                                  className="flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-1 bg-green-500 text-white rounded text-xs hover:bg-green-600"
                                >
                                  <Save className="w-3 h-3" />
                                  Save
                                </button>
                                <button
                                  onClick={cancelEditing}
                                  className="flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-1 bg-gray-500 text-white rounded text-xs hover:bg-gray-600"
                                >
                                  <X className="w-3 h-3" />
                                  Cancel
                                </button>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          ) : (
                            /* Normal Mode */
                            <div className="h-full flex flex-col">
                              <div className="flex items-start gap-3 mb-2">
                                <input
                                  type="checkbox"
                                  checked={isSelected}
                                  onChange={() => toggleGymLink(gym.id, linkType.id)}
                                  className="rounded w-5 h-5 mt-1"
                                  style={{ accentColor: theme.colors.primary }}
                                />
                                <span className="text-lg">{linkType.emoji}</span>
                                <div className="flex-1 min-w-0">
                                  <div className={`text-sm font-semibold truncate ${url ? 'text-gray-900' : 'text-gray-500'}`}>
                                    {linkType.label}
                                  </div>
                                  <div className={`text-sm ${url ? 'text-green-600' : 'text-orange-500'}`}>
                                    {url ? '‚úì Available' : 'No data'}
                                  </div>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              
                              {/* Action Buttons */}
                              <div className="flex items-center justify-end gap-1 mt-auto">
                                {url && (
                                  <>
                                    {(linkType.id === 'tuition_4_classes' || linkType.id === 'tuition_5_classes' || linkType.id === 'pricing_discount') ? (
                                      <div 
                                        className="w-3 h-3 cursor-pointer transition-colors text-xs"
                                        style={{ color: theme.colors.primary }}
                                        onClick={() => {
                                          const formattedText = url.replace(/\\n/g, '\n');
                                          alert(formattedText);
                                        }}
                                        title="View pricing"
                                      >
                                        üëÅÔ∏è
                                      </div>
                                    ) : (
                                      <ExternalLink 
                                        className="w-3 h-3 cursor-pointer transition-colors"
                                        style={{ color: theme.colors.primary }}
                                        onClick={() => window.open(url, '_blank')}
                                        title="Open link"
                                      />
                                    )}
                                    <Copy 
                                      className="w-3 h-3 text-gray-400 cursor-pointer hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors"
                                      onClick={() => {
                                        const copyText = (linkType.id === 'tuition_4_classes' || linkType.id === 'tuition_5_classes' || linkType.id === 'pricing_discount')
                                          ? url.replace(/\\n/g, '\n')
                                          : url;
                                        copyLink(copyText, linkType.label);
                                      }}
                                      title="Copy"
                                    />
                                  </>
                                )}
                                <Edit3 
                                  className="w-3 h-3 text-gray-400 cursor-pointer hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors"
                                  onClick={() => startEditingLink(gym.id, linkType.id)}
                                  title={url ? "Edit link" : "Add link"}
                                />
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          )}
                        </div>
                      );
                    })}
                  </div>
                  
                  {/* Gym Action Buttons */}
                  <div className="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-4" style={{ borderTop: '1px solid #d5c2c2' }}>
                    <button 
                      className="flex items-center gap-1 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded text-xs transition-colors"
                      style={{ backgroundColor: '#A38F85' }}
                    >
                      <Copy className="w-3 h-3" />
                      Copy Selected ({selectedGymLinks[gym.id]?.length || 0})
                    </button>
                    <button 
                      onClick={scrollToTop}
                      className="flex items-center gap-1 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 text-xs transition-colors"
                    >
                      <ArrowUp className="w-3 h-3" />
                      ‚ú® Back to Top
                    </button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
